=======
 TOPIC 
=======
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

manage the topic of a channel

| 


| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *topic-set*

    :description: set channel topic

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !topic-set Yooo
        <output> none
2) *topic*

    :description: topic [<channel>] .. get topic

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !topic
        <output> can't get topic data of channel #test



    ::

        <user> !topic #dunkbots
        <output> can't get topic data of channel #dunkbots


3) *topic-add*

    :description: topic-add <txt> .. add a topic item

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !topic-add mekker
        <output> can't get topic data


4) *topic-del*

    :description: topic-del <topicnr> .. delete topic item

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !topic-del 1
        <output> can't get topic data


5) *topic-listadd*

    :description: topic-listadd <toicnr> <person> .. add user to topiclist

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !topic-listadd 1 bart
        <output> can't get topic data


6) *topic-listdel*

    :description: topic-listdel <topicnr> <person> .. delete  user from topiclist

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !topic-listdel 1 bart
        <output> can't get topic data


7) *topic-move*

    :description: topic-move <nrfrom> <nrto> .. move topic items

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !topic-move 3 1
        <output> can't get topic data


